result.name: Foo Lum Palace

reviews.text: Beautiful and delicious restaurant with reservations
Food quality is bad. Very disappointing.

Expensive, dirty environment, rude staffs, need I say more?

Carpets are mouldy and looks like it have never been washed before. Whole place is greasy. Kitchen does not look hygienic. All in all this “palace” does not seem like a chain.
price and taste good, will visit again.
Dim sum is not warn and tea is not up to normal standard reason is added 3 rounds afterward it tease like water.

reviews.text: 晚飯🍛🍚🍝🍤🍝 服務員好好招呼👍👍👏👏
平靓正👍
招呼殷勤出品 一樓值得一試再試
一般菜式無乜特別可彈可讚，但有一樣野應該係全世界第一，响第度好難有，就係去三次著咗兩次都有真人騷表演員工大激鬥，廚房同待應丶傳菜同部長丶待應同待應...男男女女粗口橫飛，吵聲震天，肆無忌憚，目中無人，最可笑全程都唔會有人制止或勸阻，都唔知係乜制度！相信有大把食客遇過，希望嘈還嘈，千祈唔好掟野呀！🙏🙏
